HEADWORD: Can hook
<hw>Can" hook`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A device consisting of a short
rope with flat hooks at each end, for hoisting casks or barrels by the
ends of the staves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Canicula</ent>⟦br⟧
